                    "value": "<p>Urdun can establish a settlement of at least 5,000 people as his favored city by spending 1 week exploring and making contacts there. He can use his Favored City Lore skill to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Recall Knowledge] about the city; he gains a +4 circumstance bonus to his Deception and Stealth checks while in his favored city; and he applies abilities like city shepherd to his allies while in his favored city. Urdun can have only one favored city at a time (Corentyn, at the beginning of this adventure), replacing his prior settlement whenever he establishes a new favored city.</p>"
